<cb:div type="taisho-notes">
<head>大正 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0879015" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0879015">犍＝揵【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0879016" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0879016">度＋（之三）【宋】【元】【宮】，（第六之三）【明】，（七）【聖乙】</note>
<note n="0879017" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0879017">〔之一〕－【三】【宮】【聖】【聖乙】</note>
<note n="0879018" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0879018">〔復〕－【聖】【聖乙】</note>
<note n="0880001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0880001">〔耶〕－【宮】【聖乙】</note>
<note n="0880002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0880002">〔八共竟〕－【三】【宮】【聖】【聖乙】</note>
<note n="0880003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0880003">〔斷〕－【聖】【聖乙】</note>
<note n="0880004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0880004">此＝是【三】【宮】【聖】【聖乙】</note>
<note n="0880005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0880005">根＋（因）【三】【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0880006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0880006">〔無緣〕－【聖】【聖乙】</note>
<note n="0881001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0881001">〔因無色界繫〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0881002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0881002">〔無色…因〕二十四字－【三】【宮】【聖】【聖乙】</note>
<note n="0881003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0881003">〔緣欲界繫〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0881004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0881004">〔欲界繫緣〕－【聖】【聖乙】</note>
<note n="0881005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0881005">〔欲界…緣〕二十四字－【三】【宮】，欲＝色【聖】【聖乙】</note>
<note n="0881006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0881006">緣色界＝不【聖乙】</note>
<note n="0881007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0881007">色界繫＝繫緣【聖】，不繫【聖乙】</note>
<note n="0881008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0881008">緣不繫＝無緣【聖】【聖乙】</note>
<note n="0881009" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0881009">〔答曰…緣〕二十一字－【聖】【聖乙】</note>
<note n="0881010" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0881010">界＋（繫）【三】【宮】【聖】【聖乙】</note>
<note n="0882001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0882001">耶＝也【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0882002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0882002">非學＋（非學）【聖】【聖乙】</note>
<note n="0882003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0882003">〔斷〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0882004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0882004">惟＋（斷）【聖乙】</note>
<note n="0883001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0883001">上＝是【三】【宮】【聖】【聖乙】</note>
<note n="0883002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0883002">〔諦〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0883003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0883003">習＝道【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0883004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0883004">阿毘曇經卷第二十三終【聖】【聖乙】，此下聖本有光明皇后願文</note>
<note n="0883005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0883005">阿毗曇卷二十四首【聖】【聖乙】，聖本聖乙本俱前行有根犍度七緣跋第七之餘十字</note>
<note n="0883006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0883006">卷第二十三終【三】【宮】，卷末題同異如首卷，卷數下宋本元本俱有根犍度第六之二七字</note>
<note n="0883007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0883007">卷第二十四首【三】【宮】，卷題同異如首卷，前行有根犍度第六之四緣跋渠第七之餘十四字但宋本元本宮本俱無第六及第七之四字</note>
<note n="0883008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0883008">不分卷及品【三】【宮】</note>
</p>
